OL,5, US conspiracy theorist Alex Jones has  
OL,6, been ordered to pay $49.3m (#41m) in   
OL,7, damages after falsely claiming a 2012  
OL,8, school shooting was a hoax.            
OL,10,FA jury in Texas ruled the radio host   
OL,11,Fmust pay $45.2m in punitive damages, in
OL,12,Faddition to $4.1m in compensatory      
OL,13,Fdamages they awarded a day earlier.    
OL,15,FThe two-week defamation trial was      
OL,16,Fbrought by the parents of a child      
OL,17,Fkilled in the attack.                  
OL,19,FTwenty children and six adults were    
OL,20,Fkilled at Sandy Hook in Connecticut.   
